<exercise checkit-seed="0002" checkit-slug="G3" checkit-title="Eigenvalues">
  <statement>
      <p>Explain how to find the eigenvalues of the matrix <m>\left[\begin{array}{cc}
5 &amp; 2 \\
-10 &amp; -7
\end{array}\right]</m>.</p>
  </statement>
  <answer>
      <p>The characteristic polynomial of <m>\left[\begin{array}{cc}
5 &amp; 2 \\
-10 &amp; -7
\end{array}\right]</m> is <m>\lambda^{2} + 2 \lambda - 15</m>.</p>
      <p>The eigenvalues of <m>\left[\begin{array}{cc}
5 &amp; 2 \\
-10 &amp; -7
\end{array}\right]</m> are <m>3</m> and <m>-5</m>.</p>
  </answer>
</exercise>
